    "Here's a breakdown of my journey: **Early Education (Pre-Med)** I completed my undergraduate degree in biology and chemistry from a top-tier university.",
    "During this period, I was exposed to various scientific disciplines, which laid the foundation for my future studies.",
    "I was particularly drawn to the intricacies of the human brain and the complexities of the nervous system.",
    "**Medical School (MD)** I attended a prestigious medical school, where I earned my Doctor Medicine (MD) degree.",
    "The four years of medical school were intense, with a heavy emphasis on basic sciences, clinical rotations, and hospital-based training."
